                <h2>ENTERPRISE SMS PORTAL</h2>
                <p>This solution enables Corporate customers to send simultaneous text messages over the internet to Warid numbers at regular tariffs and in pre-acquired quantities through the website. An SMS Broadcast solution for Corporate subscribers who want to send text messages in relatively small quantities using a payment system based on regular rates. This option is more efficient because the broadcast volume can be adjusted according to your needs.</p>
                <h2><small>Service Features:</small></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Alphanumeric headers can be used
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Unlimited number of SMS recipients
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Create groups and manage group members  with ease and flexibility
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        An extremely user-friendly Web  Interface
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2><small>Benefits:</small></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Fast delivery time of sending message  due to broadcast message via internet
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Solutions for Corporate internal /  external coordination, and for delivering activity / product / program  information to partners and others parties
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2>BULK BROADCAST SERVICE</h2>
                <p>This service simultaneously provides the reach to complete base of Warid customers. The message is sent using a customized header and the message is relayed instantaneously to the chosen base of Warid.</p>
                <h2><small>Service Features:</small></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Alphanumeric headers can be used
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Unlimited number of SMS recipients
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Customized base can be selected based  on post/pre and geographical segregation
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2><small>Benefits:</small></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Fast delivery time of sending message  due to broadcast message via internet
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Solutions for  delivering activity / product / program  information to all of Warid active subscriber base
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2>DIRECT CONNECTION THROUGH API</h2>
                <p>This solution is meant for corporate subscribers who need SMS Broadcast solutions in order to send large quantities of SMS, using the Company’s own application. This is a more flexible option as the Company can develop the applications in line with its own needs and requirements. </p>
